  <steps>
    <step order="1">`cd src/client/shared/Spaarke.AI.Widgets/` → `npm install --legacy-peer-deps --no-audit --no-fund` → `npm run build`.</step>
    <step order="2">Capture build output (warnings + errors). File to notes/handoffs/064-build-output.md.</step>
    <step order="3">`cd src/solutions/SpaarkeAi/` → `npm install --legacy-peer-deps --no-audit --no-fund` → `npm run build`.</step>
    <step order="4">Capture build output. Append to notes/handoffs/064-build-output.md.</step>
    <step order="5">If either build fails, file diagnostic to notes/debug/064-build-failures.md with full error log; do NOT modify code (defer to follow-up task).</step>
    <step order="6">Update TASK-INDEX.md: task 064 → ✅; wave 4-A2 complete → next wave 4-B may dispatch.</step>
